sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Orch as Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>8033/TCP HTTP(S)
    participant Chunker as Caikit Chunker<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    participant Detector as Detector Services<br/>8080/TCP HTTP(S)
    participant TGIS as TGIS / Caikit NLP<br/>8033-8085/TCP gRPC
    participant OpenAI as OpenAI / vLLM<br/>8080/TCP HTTP(S)
    participant OTLP as OTLP Collector<br/>4317/TCP

    Note over Client,OTLP: Flow 1: Classification with Text Generation (v1 API)
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v1/task/classification-with-text-generation<br/>Optional TLS, Header passthrough
    Orch->>Chunker: ChunkerTokenizationTaskPredict (gRPC)<br/>Optional TLS
    Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked text segments
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents (parallel per detector)<br/>Optional TLS, Optional Bearer
    Detector-->>Orch: Input detection results
    alt Input detections trigger threshold
        Orch-->>Client: 200 OK with input detection warnings
    else Input passes
        Orch->>TGIS: Generate / TextGenerationTaskPredict (gRPC)<br/>Optional TLS
        TGIS-->>Orch: Generated text
        Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents (parallel, output)<br/>Optional TLS, Optional Bearer
        Detector-->>Orch: Output detection results
        Orch-->>Client: 200 OK with generated text + detections
    end
    Orch-)OTLP: Trace spans (async)

    Note over Client,OTLP: Flow 2: OpenAI Chat Completions with Detection (v2 API)
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>Optional TLS, Header passthrough
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/chat (input detection on last message)<br/>Optional TLS, Optional Bearer
    Detector-->>Orch: Input detection results
    alt Streaming mode
        Orch->>OpenAI: POST /v1/chat/completions (stream=true)<br/>Optional TLS, Optional Bearer
        loop SSE chunks arrive
            OpenAI-->>Orch: SSE data chunk (per choice)
            Orch->>Orch: Accumulate in CompletionState (DashMap)
            Orch->>Chunker: BidiStreamingChunkerTokenizationTaskPredict<br/>Optional TLS
            Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked output segments
            Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/generation (parallel per detector)<br/>Optional TLS, Optional Bearer
            Detector-->>Orch: Output detection batch
            Orch->>Orch: DetectionBatcherManager aggregates results
            Orch-->>Client: SSE event with chunk + detections
        end
    else Unary mode
        Orch->>OpenAI: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Optional TLS, Optional Bearer
        OpenAI-->>Orch: Complete response
        Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/generation (parallel per detector)<br/>Optional TLS, Optional Bearer
        Detector-->>Orch: Output detections
        Orch-->>Client: JSON response with detections
    end
    Orch-)OTLP: Trace spans (async)

    Note over Client,OTLP: Flow 3: Streaming Content Detection (v2 API)
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/text/detection/stream-content (ND-JSON stream)<br/>Optional TLS, Header passthrough
    loop ND-JSON chunks arrive from client
        Orch->>Chunker: BidiStreamingChunkerTokenizationTaskPredict (bidirectional)<br/>Optional TLS
        Chunker-->>Orch: Sentence-level chunks
        Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents (concurrent, batched)<br/>Optional TLS, Optional Bearer
        Detector-->>Orch: Detection results per chunk
        Orch-->>Client: ND-JSON stream with detection results
    end
    Orch-)OTLP: Trace spans (async)
